{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1340,"text":"Chris Anderson: So, this is an\ninterview with a difference."},{"time":4947,"text":"On the basis that a picture\nis worth a thousand words,"},{"time":9015,"text":"what I did was, I asked Bill and Melinda"},{"time":11911,"text":"to dig out from their archive"},{"time":14118,"text":"some images that would help explain"},{"time":16216,"text":"some of what they've done,"},{"time":17652,"text":"and do a few things that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20249,"text":"So, we're going to start here."},{"time":23980,"text":"Melinda, when and where was this,"},{"time":26183,"text":"and who is that handsome man next to you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28217,"text":"Melinda Gates: With those big glasses, huh?"},{"time":30226,"text":"This is in Africa, our very first trip,"},{"time":32265,"text":"the first time either of us had ever been to Africa,"},{"time":34170,"text":"in the fall of 1993."},{"time":35780,"text":"We were already engaged to be married."},{"time":37768,"text":"We married a few months later,"},{"time":39474,"text":"and this was the trip where we really went to see"},{"time":41691,"text":"the animals and to see the savanna."},{"time":43583,"text":"It was incredible. Bill had never taken that much time"},{"time":45571,"text":"off from work."},{"time":46983,"text":"But what really touched us, actually, were the people,"},{"time":51610,"text":"and the extreme poverty."},{"time":54218,"text":"We started asking ourselves questions."},{"time":55791,"text":"Does it have to be like this?"},{"time":57595,"text":"And at the end of the trip,"},{"time":58546,"text":"we went out to Zanzibar,"},{"time":59646,"text":"and took some time to walk on the beach,"},{"time":61134,"text":"which is something we had done a lot"},{"time":62500,"text":"while we were dating."},{"time":63818,"text":"And we'd already been talking about during that time"},{"time":66791,"text":"that the wealth that had come from Microsoft"},{"time":68648,"text":"would be given back to society,"},{"time":69923,"text":"but it was really on that beach walk"},{"time":71497,"text":"that we started to talk about, well,"},{"time":73069,"text":"what might we do and how might we go about it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76602,"text":"CA: So, given that this vacation"},{"time":79334,"text":"led to the creation of"},{"time":81526,"text":"the world's biggest private foundation,"},{"time":84342,"text":"it's pretty expensive as vacations go. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87474,"text":"MG: I guess so. We enjoyed it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89942,"text":"CA: Which of you was the key instigator here,"},{"time":92840,"text":"or was it symmetrical?"},{"time":95793,"text":"Bill Gates: Well, I think we were excited"},{"time":98186,"text":"that there'd be a phase of our life"},{"time":99653,"text":"where we'd get to work together"},{"time":101714,"text":"and figure out how to give this money back."},{"time":108325,"text":"At this stage, we were talking about the poorest,"},{"time":111474,"text":"and could you have a big impact on them?"},{"time":113876,"text":"Were there things that weren't being done?"},{"time":115801,"text":"There was a lot we didn't know."},{"time":117701,"text":"Our naïveté is pretty incredible,"},{"time":119789,"text":"when we look back on it."},{"time":120881,"text":"But we had a certain enthusiasm"},{"time":122437,"text":"that that would be the phase,"},{"time":125434,"text":"the post-Microsoft phase"},{"time":128160,"text":"would be our philanthropy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130388,"text":"MG: Which Bill always thought was going to come"},{"time":132534,"text":"after he was 60,"},{"time":133670,"text":"so he hasn't quite hit 60 yet,"},{"time":135332,"text":"so some things change along the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138525,"text":"CA: So it started there, but it got accelerated."},{"time":140969,"text":"So that was '93, and it was '97, really,"},{"time":143489,"text":"before the foundation itself started."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145227,"text":"MA: Yeah, in '97, we read an article"},{"time":147532,"text":"about diarrheal diseases killing\nso many kids around the world,"},{"time":150946,"text":"and we kept saying to ourselves,"},{"time":152560,"text":"\"Well that can't be."},{"time":153800,"text":"In the U.S., you just go down to the drug store.\""},{"time":155554,"text":"And so we started gathering scientists"},{"time":157719,"text":"and started learning about population,"},{"time":160185,"text":"learning about vaccines,"},{"time":161545,"text":"learning about what had worked and what had failed,"},{"time":163932,"text":"and that's really when we got going,"},{"time":165838,"text":"was in late 1998, 1999."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170215,"text":"CA: So, you've got a big pot of money"},{"time":172966,"text":"and a world full of so many different issues."},{"time":175293,"text":"How on Earth do you decide what to focus on?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179515,"text":"BG: Well, we decided that we'd pick two causes,"},{"time":182060,"text":"whatever the biggest inequity was globally,"},{"time":184920,"text":"and there we looked at children dying,"},{"time":187180,"text":"children not having enough nutrition to ever develop,"},{"time":189920,"text":"and countries that were really stuck,"},{"time":191419,"text":"because with that level of death,"},{"time":193679,"text":"and parents would have so many kids"},{"time":195647,"text":"that they'd get huge population growth,"},{"time":197165,"text":"and that the kids were so sick"},{"time":200291,"text":"that they really couldn't be educated"},{"time":202937,"text":"and lift themselves up."},{"time":204809,"text":"So that was our global thing,"},{"time":205917,"text":"and then in the U.S.,"},{"time":208637,"text":"both of us have had amazing educations,"},{"time":211411,"text":"and we saw that as the way that the U.S."},{"time":214460,"text":"could live up to its promise of equal opportunity"},{"time":217472,"text":"is by having a phenomenal education system,"},{"time":220057,"text":"and the more we learned, the more we realized"},{"time":222685,"text":"we're not really fulfilling that promise."},{"time":225113,"text":"And so we picked those two things,"},{"time":226950,"text":"and everything the foundation does"},{"time":228602,"text":"is focused there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231616,"text":"CA: So, I asked each of you to pick an image"},{"time":233952,"text":"that you like that illustrates your work,"},{"time":236384,"text":"and Melinda, this is what you picked."},{"time":239452,"text":"What's this about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":240919,"text":"MG: So I, one of the things I love to do when I travel"},{"time":243950,"text":"is to go out to the rural areas and talk to the women,"},{"time":247060,"text":"whether it's Bangladesh, India,\nlots of countries in Africa,"},{"time":249658,"text":"and I go in as a Western woman without a name."},{"time":252066,"text":"I don't tell them who I am. Pair of khakis."},{"time":255475,"text":"And I kept hearing from women,"},{"time":256979,"text":"over and over and over, the more I traveled,"},{"time":259862,"text":"\"I want to be able to use this shot.\""},{"time":262271,"text":"I would be there to talk to them\nabout childhood vaccines,"},{"time":264840,"text":"and they would bring the conversation around to"},{"time":267240,"text":"\"But what about the shot I get?\""},{"time":269221,"text":"which is an injection they were\ngetting called Depo-Provera,"},{"time":271673,"text":"which is a contraceptive."},{"time":273654,"text":"And I would come back and\ntalk to global health experts,"},{"time":275986,"text":"and they'd say, \"Oh no, contraceptives"},{"time":277539,"text":"are stocked in in the developing world.\""},{"time":279931,"text":"Well, you had to dig deeper into the reports,"},{"time":281921,"text":"and this is what the team came to me with,"},{"time":283697,"text":"which is, to have the number one thing"},{"time":285843,"text":"that women tell you in Africa they want to use"},{"time":288981,"text":"stocked out more than 200 days a year"},{"time":291598,"text":"explains why women were saying to me,"},{"time":293502,"text":"\"I walked 10 kilometers without\nmy husband knowing it,"},{"time":297054,"text":"and I got to the clinic, and there was nothing there.\""},{"time":300363,"text":"And so condoms were stocked in in Africa"},{"time":303170,"text":"because of all the AIDS work that the U.S."},{"time":305447,"text":"and others supported."},{"time":306851,"text":"But women will tell you over and over again,"},{"time":308522,"text":"\"I can't negotiate a condom with my husband."},{"time":311132,"text":"I'm either suggesting he has AIDS or I have AIDS,"},{"time":315340,"text":"and I need that tool because then I can space"},{"time":318100,"text":"the births of my children, and I can feed them"},{"time":320517,"text":"and have a chance of educating them.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":323055,"text":"CA: Melinda, you're Roman Catholic,"},{"time":325105,"text":"and you've often been embroiled"},{"time":328674,"text":"in controversy over this issue,"},{"time":330628,"text":"and on the abortion question,"},{"time":332877,"text":"on both sides, really."},{"time":334332,"text":"How do you navigate that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336023,"text":"MG: Yeah, so I think that's a really important point,"},{"time":339133,"text":"which is, we had backed away from contraceptives"},{"time":342216,"text":"as a global community."},{"time":343383,"text":"We knew that 210 million women"},{"time":346677,"text":"were saying they wanted access to contraceptives,"},{"time":348936,"text":"even the contraceptives we have\nhere in the United States,"},{"time":351576,"text":"and we weren't providing them"},{"time":353881,"text":"because of the political controversy in our country,"},{"time":357632,"text":"and to me that was just a crime,"},{"time":359809,"text":"and I kept looking around trying to find the person"},{"time":362574,"text":"that would get this back on the global stage,"},{"time":364924,"text":"and I finally realized I just had to do it."},{"time":366930,"text":"And even though I'm Catholic,"},{"time":368601,"text":"I believe in contraceptives"},{"time":370042,"text":"just like most of the Catholic\nwomen in the United States"},{"time":372338,"text":"who report using contraceptives,"},{"time":374169,"text":"and I shouldn't let that controversy"},{"time":376454,"text":"be the thing that holds us back."},{"time":378269,"text":"We used to have consensus in the United States"},{"time":380227,"text":"around contraceptives,"},{"time":381492,"text":"and so we got back to that global consensus,"},{"time":383972,"text":"and actually raised 2.6 billion dollars"},{"time":386616,"text":"around exactly this issue for women."},{"time":389149,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397249,"text":"CA: Bill, this is your graph. What's this about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":401105,"text":"BG: Well, my graph has numbers on it."},{"time":403090,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":405208,"text":"I really like this graph."},{"time":407025,"text":"This is the number of children"},{"time":410000,"text":"who die before the age of five every year."},{"time":412582,"text":"And what you find is really"},{"time":414405,"text":"a phenomenal success story"},{"time":416355,"text":"which is not widely known,"},{"time":418509,"text":"that we are making incredible progress."},{"time":421184,"text":"We go from 20 million"},{"time":423562,"text":"not long after I was born"},{"time":425266,"text":"to now we're down to about six million."},{"time":428952,"text":"So this is a story"},{"time":431089,"text":"largely of vaccines."},{"time":432756,"text":"Smallpox was killing a couple million kids a year."},{"time":435880,"text":"That was eradicated, so that got down to zero."},{"time":438070,"text":"Measles was killing a couple million a year."},{"time":439910,"text":"That's down to a few hundred thousand."},{"time":441613,"text":"Anyway, this is a chart"},{"time":443521,"text":"where you want to get that number to continue,"},{"time":447708,"text":"and it's going to be possible,"},{"time":449448,"text":"using the science of new vaccines,"},{"time":451124,"text":"getting the vaccines out to kids."},{"time":453016,"text":"We can actually accelerate the progress."},{"time":454740,"text":"The last decade,"},{"time":456303,"text":"that number has dropped faster"},{"time":458115,"text":"than ever in history,"},{"time":460393,"text":"and so I just love the fact that"},{"time":463116,"text":"you can say, okay, if we can invent new vaccines,"},{"time":465381,"text":"we can get them out there,"},{"time":466889,"text":"use the very latest understanding of these things,"},{"time":469374,"text":"and get the delivery right, that\nwe can perform a miracle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473985,"text":"CA: I mean, you do the math on this,"},{"time":475143,"text":"and it works out, I think, literally"},{"time":477017,"text":"to thousands of kids' lives saved every day"},{"time":479143,"text":"compared to the prior year."},{"time":481197,"text":"It's not reported."},{"time":483044,"text":"An airliner with 200-plus deaths"},{"time":486290,"text":"is a far, far bigger story than that."},{"time":488500,"text":"Does that drive you crazy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":490049,"text":"BG: Yeah, because it's a silent thing going on."},{"time":493040,"text":"It's a kid, one kid at a time."},{"time":495710,"text":"Ninety-eight percent of this"},{"time":497173,"text":"has nothing to do with natural disasters,"},{"time":499050,"text":"and yet, people's charity,"},{"time":500527,"text":"when they see a natural disaster, are wonderful."},{"time":502050,"text":"It's incredible how people think, okay,"},{"time":504286,"text":"that could be me, and the money flows."},{"time":507062,"text":"These causes have been a bit invisible."},{"time":510468,"text":"Now that the Millennium Development Goals"},{"time":512679,"text":"and various things are getting out there,"},{"time":514229,"text":"we are seeing some increased generosity,"},{"time":517073,"text":"so the goal is to get this well below a million,"},{"time":520344,"text":"which should be possible in our lifetime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522762,"text":"CA: Maybe it needed someone"},{"time":523942,"text":"who is turned on by numbers and graphs"},{"time":526038,"text":"rather than just the big, sad face"},{"time":528452,"text":"to get engaged."},{"time":530107,"text":"I mean, you've used it in your letter this year,"},{"time":531830,"text":"you used basically this argument to say that aid,"},{"time":535281,"text":"contrary to the current meme"},{"time":536952,"text":"that aid is kind of worthless and broken,"},{"time":540035,"text":"that actually it has been effective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541988,"text":"BG: Yeah, well people can take,"},{"time":543968,"text":"there is some aid that was well-meaning"},{"time":547148,"text":"and didn't go well."},{"time":549071,"text":"There's some venture capital investments"},{"time":551004,"text":"that were well-meaning and didn't go well."},{"time":553904,"text":"You shouldn't just say, okay, because of that,"},{"time":556743,"text":"because we don't have a perfect record,"},{"time":559861,"text":"this is a bad endeavor."},{"time":561393,"text":"You should look at, what was your goal?"},{"time":563263,"text":"How are you trying to uplift nutrition"},{"time":565871,"text":"and survival and literacy"},{"time":569275,"text":"so these countries can take care of themselves,"},{"time":570910,"text":"and say wow, this is going well,"},{"time":572914,"text":"and be smarter."},{"time":574186,"text":"We can spend aid smarter."},{"time":576026,"text":"It is not all a panacea."},{"time":579438,"text":"We can do better than venture capital, I think,"},{"time":582370,"text":"including big hits like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585157,"text":"CA: Traditional wisdom is that"},{"time":587900,"text":"it's pretty hard for married couples to work together."},{"time":591948,"text":"How have you guys managed it?"},{"time":593564,"text":"MG: Yeah, I've had a lot of women say to me,"},{"time":595234,"text":"\"I really don't think I could work with my husband."},{"time":597093,"text":"That just wouldn't work out.\""},{"time":599240,"text":"You know, we enjoy it, and we don't --"},{"time":602829,"text":"this foundation has been a coming to for both of us"},{"time":605315,"text":"in its continuous learning journey,"},{"time":608143,"text":"and we don't travel together as much"},{"time":610902,"text":"for the foundation, actually, as we used to"},{"time":612830,"text":"when Bill was working at Microsoft."},{"time":614286,"text":"We have more trips where\nwe're traveling separately,"},{"time":616509,"text":"but I always know when I come home,"},{"time":618651,"text":"Bill's going to be interested in what I learned,"},{"time":620790,"text":"whether it's about women or girls"},{"time":622533,"text":"or something new about the vaccine delivery chain,"},{"time":625219,"text":"or this person that is a great leader."},{"time":627455,"text":"He's going to listen and be really interested."},{"time":629922,"text":"And he knows when he comes home,"},{"time":631525,"text":"even if it's to talk about the speech he did"},{"time":633358,"text":"or the data or what he's learned,"},{"time":635100,"text":"I'm really interested,"},{"time":636342,"text":"and I think we have a really\ncollaborative relationship."},{"time":639242,"text":"But we don't every minute together, that's for sure."},{"time":641916,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":646091,"text":"CA: But now you are, and we're very happy that you are."},{"time":648586,"text":"Melinda, early on, you were basically"},{"time":652172,"text":"largely running the show."},{"time":654173,"text":"Six years ago, I guess,"},{"time":655385,"text":"Bill came on full time, so moved from Microsoft"},{"time":657968,"text":"and became full time."},{"time":659079,"text":"That must have been hard,"},{"time":660058,"text":"adjusting to that. No?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":662094,"text":"MG: Yeah. I think actually,"},{"time":665148,"text":"for the foundation employees,"},{"time":667137,"text":"there was way more angst for them"},{"time":669684,"text":"than there was for me about Bill coming."},{"time":671050,"text":"I was actually really excited."},{"time":672256,"text":"I mean, Bill made this decision"},{"time":673875,"text":"even obviously before it got announced in 2006,"},{"time":676558,"text":"and it was really his decision,"},{"time":678260,"text":"but again, it was a beach vacation"},{"time":680146,"text":"where we were walking on the beach"},{"time":681450,"text":"and he was starting to think of this idea."},{"time":683714,"text":"And for me, the excitement of Bill"},{"time":686326,"text":"putting his brain and his heart"},{"time":689035,"text":"against these huge global problems,"},{"time":691382,"text":"these inequities, to me that was exciting."},{"time":693710,"text":"Yes, the foundation employees had angst about that."},{"time":697444,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":699119,"text":"CA: That's cool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":701235,"text":"MG: But that went away within three months,"},{"time":702919,"text":"once he was there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703846,"text":"BG: Including some of the employees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705511,"text":"MG: That's what I said, the employees,"},{"time":706784,"text":"it went away for them three\nmonths after you were there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":708906,"text":"BG: No, I'm kidding.\nMG: Oh, you mean, the employees didn't go away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711226,"text":"BG: A few of them did, but —"},{"time":713127,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":714960,"text":"CA: So what do you guys argue about?"},{"time":716903,"text":"Sunday, 11 o'clock,"},{"time":719560,"text":"you're away from work,"},{"time":720981,"text":"what comes up? What's the argument?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":723494,"text":"BG: Because we built this thing"},{"time":725139,"text":"together from the beginning,"},{"time":728258,"text":"it's this great partnership."},{"time":729904,"text":"I had that with Paul Allen"},{"time":731758,"text":"in the early days of Microsoft."},{"time":733669,"text":"I had it with Steve Ballmer as Microsoft got bigger,"},{"time":736481,"text":"and now Melinda, and in even stronger,"},{"time":739485,"text":"equal ways, is the partner,"},{"time":741371,"text":"so we talk a lot about"},{"time":743128,"text":"which things should we give more to,"},{"time":745256,"text":"which groups are working well?"},{"time":747800,"text":"She's got a lot of insight."},{"time":749053,"text":"She'll sit down with the employees a lot."},{"time":750700,"text":"We'll take the different trips she described."},{"time":752816,"text":"So there's a lot of collaboration."},{"time":756433,"text":"I can't think of anything where one of us"},{"time":758409,"text":"had a super strong opinion"},{"time":761679,"text":"about one thing or another?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":763515,"text":"CA: How about you, Melinda, \nthough? Can you? (Laughter)"},{"time":766317,"text":"You never know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767533,"text":"MG: Well, here's the thing."},{"time":769059,"text":"We come at things from different angles,"},{"time":770798,"text":"and I actually think that's really good."},{"time":772730,"text":"So Bill can look at the big data"},{"time":774738,"text":"and say, \"I want to act based\non these global statistics.\""},{"time":777750,"text":"For me, I come at it from intuition."},{"time":779616,"text":"I meet with lots of people on the ground"},{"time":781549,"text":"and Bill's taught me to take that"},{"time":783529,"text":"and read up to the global data and see if they match,"},{"time":786152,"text":"and I think what I've taught him"},{"time":787241,"text":"is to take that data"},{"time":788669,"text":"and meet with people on the ground to understand,"},{"time":790283,"text":"can you actually deliver that vaccine?"},{"time":792667,"text":"Can you get a woman to accept those polio drops"},{"time":795868,"text":"in her child's mouth?"},{"time":797198,"text":"Because the delivery piece"},{"time":798756,"text":"is every bit as important as the science."},{"time":800959,"text":"So I think it's been more a coming to over time"},{"time":803481,"text":"towards each other's point of view,"},{"time":804776,"text":"and quite frankly, the work is better because of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":808046,"text":"CA: So, in vaccines and polio and so forth,"},{"time":810319,"text":"you've had some amazing successes."},{"time":814118,"text":"What about failure, though?"},{"time":815350,"text":"Can you talk about a failure"},{"time":817041,"text":"and maybe what you've learned from it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":819137,"text":"BG: Yeah. Fortunately, we can afford a few failures,"},{"time":821705,"text":"because we've certainly had them."},{"time":823842,"text":"We do a lot of drug work or vaccine work"},{"time":828216,"text":"that you know you're going to have different failures."},{"time":831492,"text":"Like, we put out, one that got a lot of publicity"},{"time":833719,"text":"was asking for a better condom."},{"time":835020,"text":"Well, we got hundreds of ideas."},{"time":836514,"text":"Maybe a few of those will work out."},{"time":839708,"text":"We were very naïve, certainly I was, about a drug"},{"time":843087,"text":"for a disease in India, visceral leishmaniasis,"},{"time":845703,"text":"that I thought, once I got this drug,"},{"time":847354,"text":"we can just go wipe out the disease."},{"time":848710,"text":"Well, turns out it took an injection"},{"time":851290,"text":"every day for 10 days."},{"time":852926,"text":"It took three more years to get it than we expected,"},{"time":855313,"text":"and then there was no way"},{"time":856771,"text":"it was going to get out there."},{"time":859139,"text":"Fortunately, we found out"},{"time":860358,"text":"that if you go kill the sand flies,"},{"time":863520,"text":"you probably can have success there,"},{"time":865642,"text":"but we spent five years,"},{"time":867497,"text":"you could say wasted five years,"},{"time":868875,"text":"and about 60 million,"},{"time":870882,"text":"on a path that turned out to have"},{"time":872222,"text":"very modest benefit when we got there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":876387,"text":"CA: You're spending, like, a billion dollars a year"},{"time":879831,"text":"in education, I think, something like that."},{"time":881766,"text":"Is anything, the story of what's gone right there"},{"time":885790,"text":"is quite a long and complex one."},{"time":888246,"text":"Are there any failures that you can talk about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":892168,"text":"MG: Well, I would say a huge lesson for us"},{"time":893958,"text":"out of the early work is we thought"},{"time":895206,"text":"that these small schools were the answer,"},{"time":897739,"text":"and small schools definitely help."},{"time":899209,"text":"They bring down the dropout rate."},{"time":900733,"text":"They have less violence and crime in those schools."},{"time":903333,"text":"But the thing that we learned from that work,"},{"time":905479,"text":"and what turned out to be the fundamental key,"},{"time":908013,"text":"is a great teacher in front of the classroom."},{"time":910077,"text":"If you don't have an effective teacher"},{"time":911684,"text":"in the front of the classroom,"},{"time":912750,"text":"I don't care how big or small the building is,"},{"time":914906,"text":"you're not going to change the trajectory"},{"time":916560,"text":"of whether that student will be ready for college."},{"time":918513,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":923108,"text":"CA: So Melinda, this is you and"},{"time":925418,"text":"your eldest daughter, Jenn."},{"time":928972,"text":"And just taken about three weeks ago, I think,"},{"time":930871,"text":"three or four weeks ago. Where was this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":932455,"text":"MG: So we went to Tanzania."},{"time":934211,"text":"Jenn's been to Tanzania."},{"time":935053,"text":"All our kids have been to Africa quite a bit, actually."},{"time":937756,"text":"And we did something very different,"},{"time":939971,"text":"which is, we decided to go spend"},{"time":941798,"text":"two nights and three days with a family."},{"time":944217,"text":"Anna and Sanare are the parents."},{"time":947318,"text":"They invited us to come and stay in their boma."},{"time":950352,"text":"Actually, the goats had been there, I think,"},{"time":951851,"text":"living in that particular little hut"},{"time":953250,"text":"on their little compound before we got there."},{"time":955921,"text":"And we stayed with their family,"},{"time":957419,"text":"and we really, really learned"},{"time":959353,"text":"what life is like in rural Tanzania."},{"time":961206,"text":"And the difference between just going"},{"time":962820,"text":"and visiting for half a day"},{"time":964539,"text":"or three quarters of a day"},{"time":966001,"text":"versus staying overnight was profound,"},{"time":968399,"text":"and so let me just give you one explanation of that."},{"time":971890,"text":"They had six children, and as I talked to Anna"},{"time":974019,"text":"in the kitchen, we cooked for about five hours"},{"time":975794,"text":"in the cooking hut that day,"},{"time":977437,"text":"and as I talked to her, she had absolutely planned"},{"time":979248,"text":"and spaced with her husband"},{"time":980718,"text":"the births of their children."},{"time":982155,"text":"It was a very loving relationship."},{"time":983810,"text":"This was a Maasai warrior and his wife,"},{"time":986113,"text":"but they had decided to get married,"},{"time":988022,"text":"they clearly had respect and love in the relationship."},{"time":991357,"text":"Their children, their six children,"},{"time":992968,"text":"the two in the middle were twins, 13,"},{"time":995487,"text":"a boy, and a girl named Grace."},{"time":997740,"text":"And when we'd go out to chop wood"},{"time":999313,"text":"and do all the things that Grace\nand her mother would do,"},{"time":1001748,"text":"Grace was not a child, she was an adolescent,"},{"time":1004340,"text":"but she wasn't an adult."},{"time":1005817,"text":"She was very, very shy."},{"time":1007568,"text":"So she kept wanting to talk to me and Jenn."},{"time":1009329,"text":"We kept trying to engage her, but she was shy."},{"time":1012164,"text":"And at night, though,"},{"time":1013770,"text":"when all the lights went out in rural Tanzania,"},{"time":1016577,"text":"and there was no moon that night,"},{"time":1018081,"text":"the first night, and no stars,"},{"time":1019803,"text":"and Jenn came out of our hut"},{"time":1021629,"text":"with her REI little headlamp on,"},{"time":1024446,"text":"Grace went immediately,"},{"time":1026584,"text":"and got the translator,"},{"time":1027940,"text":"came straight up to my Jenn and said,"},{"time":1030030,"text":"\"When you go home,"},{"time":1031263,"text":"can I have your headlamp"},{"time":1032438,"text":"so I can study at night?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1034168,"text":"CA: Oh, wow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035250,"text":"MG: And her dad had told me"},{"time":1036734,"text":"how afraid he was that unlike the son,"},{"time":1038821,"text":"who had passed his secondary exams,"},{"time":1040483,"text":"because of her chores,"},{"time":1042013,"text":"she'd not done so well"},{"time":1043451,"text":"and wasn't in the government school yet."},{"time":1045255,"text":"He said, \"I don't know how I'm\ngoing to pay for her education."},{"time":1047790,"text":"I can't pay for private school,"},{"time":1049616,"text":"and she may end up on this farm like my wife.\""},{"time":1052195,"text":"So they know the difference"},{"time":1053324,"text":"that an education can make"},{"time":1054349,"text":"in a huge, profound way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1057346,"text":"CA: I mean, this is another pic"},{"time":1058767,"text":"of your other two kids, Rory and Phoebe,"},{"time":1062173,"text":"along with Paul Farmer."},{"time":1066311,"text":"Bringing up three children"},{"time":1067925,"text":"when you're the world's richest family"},{"time":1070927,"text":"seems like a social experiment"},{"time":1073223,"text":"without much prior art."},{"time":1076795,"text":"How have you managed it?"},{"time":1078330,"text":"What's been your approach?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1080545,"text":"BG: Well, I'd say overall"},{"time":1083178,"text":"the kids get a great education,"},{"time":1084940,"text":"but you've got to make sure"},{"time":1085838,"text":"they have a sense of their own ability"},{"time":1087540,"text":"and what they're going to go and do,"},{"time":1089529,"text":"and our philosophy has been"},{"time":1091902,"text":"to be very clear with them --"},{"time":1093124,"text":"most of the money's going to the foundation --"},{"time":1094669,"text":"and help them find something they're excited about."},{"time":1099010,"text":"We want to strike a balance where they have"},{"time":1100405,"text":"the freedom to do anything"},{"time":1102198,"text":"but not a lot of money showered on them"},{"time":1105538,"text":"so they could go out and do nothing."},{"time":1108667,"text":"And so far, they're fairly diligent,"},{"time":1111645,"text":"excited to pick their own direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1114853,"text":"CA: You've obviously guarded their \nprivacy carefully for obvious reasons."},{"time":1120421,"text":"I'm curious why you've given me permission"},{"time":1122615,"text":"to show this picture now here at TED."},{"time":1124240,"text":"MG: Well, it's interesting."},{"time":1125377,"text":"As they get older, they so know"},{"time":1127218,"text":"that our family belief is about responsibility,"},{"time":1130227,"text":"that we are in an unbelievable situation"},{"time":1132342,"text":"just to live in the United States"},{"time":1133960,"text":"and have a great education,"},{"time":1135651,"text":"and we have a responsibility\nto give back to the world."},{"time":1137699,"text":"And so as they get older"},{"time":1138752,"text":"and we are teaching them --"},{"time":1139772,"text":"they have been to so many\ncountries around the world —"},{"time":1142132,"text":"they're saying,"},{"time":1143264,"text":"we do want people to know that we believe"},{"time":1145016,"text":"in what you're doing, Mom and Dad,"},{"time":1146517,"text":"and it is okay to show us more."},{"time":1148478,"text":"So we have their permission to show this picture,"},{"time":1151130,"text":"and I think Paul Farmer is probably going to put it"},{"time":1152845,"text":"eventually in some of his work."},{"time":1155300,"text":"But they really care deeply"},{"time":1156902,"text":"about the mission of the foundation, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1159327,"text":"CA: You've easily got enough money"},{"time":1161249,"text":"despite your vast contributions to the foundation"},{"time":1163840,"text":"to make them all billionaires."},{"time":1165474,"text":"Is that your plan for them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1166991,"text":"BG: Nope. No. They won't have anything like that."},{"time":1169327,"text":"They need to have a sense"},{"time":1171262,"text":"that their own work is meaningful and important."},{"time":1177798,"text":"We read an article long, actually,\nbefore we got married,"},{"time":1181270,"text":"where Warren Buffett talked about that,"},{"time":1183915,"text":"and we're quite convinced that it wasn't a favor"},{"time":1186164,"text":"either to society or to the kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1189418,"text":"CA: Well, speaking of Warren Buffett,"},{"time":1191486,"text":"something really amazing happened in 2006,"},{"time":1194150,"text":"when somehow your only real rival"},{"time":1197110,"text":"for richest person in America"},{"time":1198662,"text":"suddenly turned around and agreed to give"},{"time":1200032,"text":"80 percent of his fortune"},{"time":1202625,"text":"to your foundation."},{"time":1204342,"text":"How on Earth did that happen?"},{"time":1206078,"text":"I guess there's a long version\nand a short version of that."},{"time":1208056,"text":"We've got time for the short version."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1209438,"text":"BG: All right. Well, Warren was a close friend,"},{"time":1213193,"text":"and he was going to have his wife Suzie"},{"time":1217850,"text":"give it all away."},{"time":1219405,"text":"Tragically, she passed away before he did,"},{"time":1222846,"text":"and he's big on delegation, and"},{"time":1226444,"text":"— (Laughter) —"},{"time":1228602,"text":"he said —"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1230013,"text":"CA: Tweet that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1230868,"text":"BG: If he's got somebody\nwho is doing something well,"},{"time":1234029,"text":"and is willing to do it at no charge,"},{"time":1238486,"text":"maybe that's okay. But we were stunned."},{"time":1240864,"text":"MG: Totally stunned.\nBG: We had never expected it,"},{"time":1242960,"text":"and it has been unbelievable."},{"time":1244525,"text":"It's allowed us to increase our ambition"},{"time":1247665,"text":"in what the foundation can do quite dramatically."},{"time":1251282,"text":"Half the resources we have"},{"time":1252786,"text":"come from Warren's mind-blowing generosity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1255670,"text":"CA: And I think you've pledged that"},{"time":1256554,"text":"by the time you're done,"},{"time":1258344,"text":"more than, or 95 percent of your wealth,"},{"time":1260222,"text":"will be given to the foundation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1262117,"text":"BG: Yes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1263271,"text":"CA: And since this relationship, it's amazing—"},{"time":1267020,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":1270386,"text":"And recently, you and Warren"},{"time":1273023,"text":"have been going around trying to persuade"},{"time":1274903,"text":"other billionaires and successful people"},{"time":1276879,"text":"to pledge to give, what,"},{"time":1278402,"text":"more than half of their assets for philanthropy."},{"time":1284160,"text":"How is that going?"},{"time":1286575,"text":"BG: Well, we've got about 120 people"},{"time":1289747,"text":"who have now taken this giving pledge."},{"time":1292185,"text":"The thing that's great is that we get together"},{"time":1294791,"text":"yearly and talk about, okay,"},{"time":1296900,"text":"do you hire staff, what do you give to them?"},{"time":1298865,"text":"We're not trying to homogenize it."},{"time":1300092,"text":"I mean, the beauty of philanthropy"},{"time":1301140,"text":"is this mind-blowing diversity."},{"time":1303147,"text":"People give to some things."},{"time":1304310,"text":"We look and go, \"Wow.\""},{"time":1306989,"text":"But that's great."},{"time":1308097,"text":"That's the role of philanthropy"},{"time":1309226,"text":"is to pick different approaches,"},{"time":1311713,"text":"including even in one space, like education."},{"time":1313705,"text":"We need more experimentation."},{"time":1316076,"text":"But it's been wonderful, meeting those people,"},{"time":1318980,"text":"sharing their journey to philanthropy,"},{"time":1321212,"text":"how they involve their kids,"},{"time":1322316,"text":"where they're doing it differently,"},{"time":1324150,"text":"and it's been way more successful than we expected."},{"time":1326856,"text":"Now it looks like it'll just keep growing in size"},{"time":1329551,"text":"in the years ahead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1332114,"text":"MG: And having people see that other people"},{"time":1335626,"text":"are making change with philanthropy,"},{"time":1337330,"text":"I mean, these are people who have"},{"time":1339666,"text":"created their own businesses,"},{"time":1340711,"text":"put their own ingenuity behind incredible ideas."},{"time":1343359,"text":"If they put their ideas and their brain"},{"time":1345585,"text":"behind philanthropy, they can change the world."},{"time":1348118,"text":"And they start to see others doing it, and saying,"},{"time":1350409,"text":"\"Wow, I want to do that with my own money.\""},{"time":1352449,"text":"To me, that's the piece that's incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1354493,"text":"CA: It seems to me, it's actually really hard"},{"time":1357411,"text":"for some people to figure out"},{"time":1358657,"text":"even how to remotely spend that much money"},{"time":1361340,"text":"on something else."},{"time":1363513,"text":"There are probably some billionaires in the room"},{"time":1365606,"text":"and certainly some successful people."},{"time":1367715,"text":"I'm curious, can you make the pitch?"},{"time":1369775,"text":"What's the pitch?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1371009,"text":"BG: Well, it's the most fulfilling thing"},{"time":1372390,"text":"we've ever done,"},{"time":1373872,"text":"and you can't take it with you,"},{"time":1376842,"text":"and if it's not good for your kids,"},{"time":1380024,"text":"let's get together and brainstorm"},{"time":1381313,"text":"about what we can be done."},{"time":1384000,"text":"The world is a far better place"},{"time":1386190,"text":"because of the philanthropists of the past,"},{"time":1388828,"text":"and the U.S. tradition here, which is the strongest,"},{"time":1391861,"text":"is the envy of the world."},{"time":1393212,"text":"And part of the reason I'm so optimistic"},{"time":1395130,"text":"is because I do think philanthropy"},{"time":1397074,"text":"is going to grow"},{"time":1398688,"text":"and take some of these things"},{"time":1399807,"text":"government's not just good at\nworking on and discovering"},{"time":1402706,"text":"and shine some light in the right direction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1406176,"text":"CA: The world's got this terrible inequality,"},{"time":1409118,"text":"growing inequality problem"},{"time":1410279,"text":"that seems structural."},{"time":1411740,"text":"It does seem to me that if more of your peers"},{"time":1414606,"text":"took the approach that you two have made,"},{"time":1416982,"text":"it would make a dent"},{"time":1418574,"text":"both in that problem and certainly"},{"time":1419840,"text":"in the perception of that problem."},{"time":1421440,"text":"Is that a fair comment?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1422844,"text":"BG: Oh yeah. If you take from the most wealthy"},{"time":1424502,"text":"and give to the least wealthy, it's good."},{"time":1427834,"text":"It tries to balance out, and that's just."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1429966,"text":"MG: But you change systems."},{"time":1431722,"text":"In the U.S., we're trying to\nchange the education system"},{"time":1434335,"text":"so it's just for everybody"},{"time":1436403,"text":"and it works for all students."},{"time":1437960,"text":"That, to me, really changes"},{"time":1439850,"text":"the inequality balance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1441007,"text":"BG: That's the most important."},{"time":1442589,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1446137,"text":"CA: Well, I really think that most people here"},{"time":1449552,"text":"and many millions around the world"},{"time":1451297,"text":"are just in awe of the trajectory"},{"time":1453846,"text":"your lives have taken"},{"time":1455154,"text":"and the spectacular degree to which"},{"time":1458885,"text":"you have shaped the future."},{"time":1461000,"text":"Thank you so much for coming to TED"},{"time":1462340,"text":"and for sharing with us and for all you do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1463801,"text":"BG: Thank you.\nMG: Thank you."},{"time":1465737,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1474515,"text":"BG: Thank you.\nMG: Thank you very much."},{"time":1478910,"text":"BG: All right, good job. (Applause)"}]}]}